      <title>爱尔兰计划简化国防规则以支持乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ireland-plans-to-ease-defense-rules-to-support-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰政府将提出更改其在国外派遣部队的规则，因为中立国家加大了对乌克兰的实际支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ireland-plans-to-ease-defense-rules-to-support-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 10:01:36 GMT</pubDate>
